# Codex session excerpt: three Q&A pairs after the runtime/module_runner prompt
# Source: /Users/shenjiachen/.codex/sessions/2026/07/10/rollout-2026-07-10T10-42-03-019f49e7-4fd2-7981-a905-ca76ad60e8ff.jsonl
